_sText:
This map was made in a snowy theme, and is quite big.

Maptype: Awp
Number of Player: 32 (recommended 24)

Most boxes are customly made into icecubes just for the beauty of it.
There is also falling snow, to give players the feel of being in the cold.

I can't really say much about it, you just gotta try it yourself :)

Please inform me of bugs found or anything that you wish to be included. I might make a v2.

Thanks and have fun!
